
        OBJECT CREATION
* There may be variables and methods in a Class. If we want to use these variables and methods, we should create an Object.

* We can reach variables and methods in a Class thanks to the created Object in another Class.

* How to create an Object?
        Class Name    Object Name     Assignment Operator     "new" keyword       Constructor
           Car          myCar                =                     new               Car();

* Scanner is a Class that we get data from user and we use these data in our codes.

* We should follow 4 steps when using Scanner Class.
    1. Create Scanner Object
    2. Give message to the user
    3. Put the data comes from the user into memory using appropriate method
    4. Use the data in memory in our codes